{"word":"ἀφρόνιτρον","slug":"ἀφρόνιτρον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n18529\" key=\"a)fro/nitron\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀφρόνιτρον</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀφρόλιτρον</orth> (the two distd. by Gal.l.c., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gp.\">Gp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.28</biblScope> </bibl>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, a form of <sense id=\"n18529.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">native sodium carbonate</tr_> (cf.<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νίτρον</foreign>), distd. by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.212</biblScope> </bibl> from the finer <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄνθος νίτρου,</foreign> cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Herod.Med.\">Herod.Med.</a></author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg001:6:20:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orib.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.20.5</biblScope> </bibl>: in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> </bibl> and correct Greek divisim <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀφρὸς νίτρου</foreign>: hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀφρόνιτρον</foreign> is condemned by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phryn.</author> <biblScope TEIform